{"article_id":"D3KzTSvpNaWu185o","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"And that ' s what Trump is asking of Congress .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"He knows","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that Obama did nothing wrong .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Spicer knows","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that Obama did nothing wrong .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"But Trump is obsessed with President Obama .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"He ' s obsessed with Obama ' s accomplishments , with his popularity , with how many , many , many more people showed up","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to celebrate Obama ' s inauguration .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Asking Congress to \" investigate \" the non-existent wiretapping is just asking Chaffetz , Gowdy , and company to spend millions","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"trying to hurt Barack Obama ' s reputation","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"the way","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"they did Hillary Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"What has Trump ' s staff produced","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"to demonstrate","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"that there ' s anything to his Breitbart-fueled accusations ?","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"\" No , that ' s above my pay grade , \"","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"said Sean Spicer , the White House press secretary and a feisty Trump loyalist ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"when asked on Tuesday at an on-camera briefing","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"if he had seen any evidence","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to back up Mr. Trump ' s accusation .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The reporters kept at him ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"but Mr. Spicer pointedly and repeatedly refused to offer personal assurances","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that the president ' s statements were true .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"\" No comment , \"","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Attorney General Jeff Sessions said earlier in the day .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Last week , Mr . Sessions recused himself from any investigations","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"involving the Trump campaign ' s contacts with Russia .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"\" I don ' t know anything about it , \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"John F. Kelly , the homeland security secretary , said on CNN on Monday .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Mr. Kelly shrugged","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and added","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"\" if the president of the United States said that ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"he ' s got his reasons","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"to say it . \"","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"Yes .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Yes he does .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Those reasons are the same ones","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"that drove Trump to say","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that President Obama was born in Kenya","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and to go on about what his investigators had \" discovered \" about Obama","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"long after other Obama-haters had let this ultimately idiotic position drop .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Former President Obama was reportedly furious","depth":4},{"id":43,"text":"after President Trump fired off tweets","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"accusing him of wiretapping Trump Tower before the presidential election ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"according to a new report .","depth":3},{"id":46,"text":"Barack Obama is not running for anything .","depth":3},{"id":47,"text":"And he ' s not going to stay quiet forever .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":95,"left":89,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":59,"right":88,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":59,"left":0,"right":58,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":54,"right":57,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":54,"left":51,"right":53,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":51,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":49,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{